00:32:38,927 --> 00:32:40,637
Senjata Pasukan Khusus AS.

291
00:32:42,222 --> 00:32:44,807
- Chambers.
- Jump Chambers?

292
00:32:44,891 --> 00:32:46,017
Kuharap bukan.

293
00:32:48,561 --> 00:32:51,606
