415
00:42:05,058 --> 00:42:06,894
Jika aku tak beri permatanya,
dia akan mati.

416
00:42:11,690 --> 00:42:13,859
Apa yang kau inginkan, Kawan? Maksudku...

417
00:42:18,864 --> 00:42:21,992
