425
00:42:53,943 --> 00:42:56,529
- Buat saja lagi.
- Berengsek kau.

426
00:42:58,197 --> 00:42:59,365
Drama.

427
00:43:00,700 --> 00:43:02,326
Si orang Tionghoa tak bodoh.

428
00:43:05,162 --> 00:43:07,707
Buatlah keturunan lebih banyak lagi.

429
00:43:08,749 --> 00:43:10,418
